@MulhollandRealEstate.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5278

### List tickets
GET {{MulhollandRealEstate.API_HostAddress}}/api/tickets

### Summary
GET {{MulhollandRealEstate.API_HostAddress}}/api/tickets/summary

### Triage one ticket
POST {{MulhollandRealEstate.API_HostAddress}}/api/tickets/1001/triage

### Triage all (batch)
POST {{MulhollandRealEstate.API_HostAddress}}/api/tickets/triage-all
